WEBVTT

01:32.190 --> 01:34.990
[How dare you!?]

01:35.039 --> 01:37.970
[Episode 29]

01:41.000 --> 01:41.430
Chu Si?

01:41.789 --> 01:42.280
Chu Qi?

02:11.110 --> 02:11.710
Wait here.

02:12.120 --> 02:13.580
I'll go ask her right away.

02:16.360 --> 02:17.220
Your Highness?

02:19.710 --> 02:21.370
Your Highness, why are you...

02:23.620 --> 02:25.190
I was looking for my secret guards.

02:25.190 --> 02:25.920
Don't worry.

02:26.190 --> 02:27.250
It's cold outside.

02:27.630 --> 02:28.680
Your Highness, why don't you

02:28.680 --> 02:30.110
return to your tent and rest?

02:30.110 --> 02:32.770
I'll send someone to
look for them immediately.

02:33.150 --> 02:34.950
May I wait in your tent, General?

02:43.829 --> 02:45.160
Please, Your Highness.

02:51.280 --> 02:52.010
It's so late.

02:52.730 --> 02:55.460
Why did Your Highness come out
dressed so thinly?

03:03.940 --> 03:04.360
Here,

03:05.150 --> 03:06.210
have some warm tea.

03:07.080 --> 03:07.550
No need.

03:07.580 --> 03:08.180
Thank you.

03:10.510 --> 03:12.570
Were you talking to someone just now?

03:13.710 --> 03:14.430
Just now?

03:15.250 --> 03:16.710
I was alone the whole time.

03:39.370 --> 03:40.230
Your Highness,

03:40.900 --> 03:43.560
there's something
I've been meaning to ask you.

03:43.890 --> 03:44.480
Go ahead.

03:50.290 --> 03:52.150
We're about to reach the capital.

03:52.680 --> 03:53.190
By then,

03:54.310 --> 03:55.970
there will be no turning back.

03:57.000 --> 03:58.130
If you want to leave,

03:58.750 --> 04:00.150
this is your last chance.

04:00.800 --> 04:02.400
I can take you to a safe place.

04:03.120 --> 04:04.720
You could have your own life—

04:05.210 --> 04:07.140
you wouldn't have to bear all this.

04:11.470 --> 04:12.470
If I don't bear it,

04:13.800 --> 04:14.800
then who will?

04:17.510 --> 04:17.950
You?

04:20.190 --> 04:21.190
I've told you that

04:22.300 --> 04:23.300
I have no interest

04:25.040 --> 04:26.040
in state affairs.

04:31.120 --> 04:31.920
Then who is it?

04:33.260 --> 04:33.600
Your Highness!

04:33.600 --> 04:35.600
Is there anyone else in charge here?

05:06.360 --> 05:07.760
With so many people here,

05:10.040 --> 05:11.500
don't you find it cramped?

05:13.080 --> 05:14.070
♪ Tell me ♪

05:13.710 --> 05:14.470
Let's go.

05:14.730 --> 05:18.190
♪ Why so many laments echo in the wind ♪

05:15.190 --> 05:16.120
Com on, let's go.

05:19.800 --> 05:20.950
♪ Walk past me ♪

05:21.250 --> 05:25.010
♪ Like an aloof passerby ♪

05:26.340 --> 05:28.880
♪ Don't watch me as the rain falls ♪

05:29.650 --> 05:32.470
♪ Love burns too hot as it passes ♪

05:33.200 --> 05:39.060
♪ Even a lifetime of war
cannot be extinguished ♪

05:40.010 --> 05:41.110
♪ Blame me ♪

05:41.800 --> 05:45.400
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

05:43.750 --> 05:45.120
As Bai just said,

05:46.860 --> 05:48.140
♪ Hide me ♪

05:47.030 --> 05:48.159
if you want to leave,

05:48.550 --> 05:52.460
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

05:49.720 --> 05:50.310
now

05:51.630 --> 05:52.760
is the last chance.

05:53.750 --> 05:56.220
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

05:54.560 --> 05:55.090
Alright.

05:57.080 --> 05:59.750
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

05:57.190 --> 05:58.650
If this is what you want,

06:00.070 --> 06:00.920
I'll leave.

06:00.620 --> 06:03.610
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

06:03.690 --> 06:05.750
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

06:05.760 --> 06:06.270
Wanyin.

06:06.140 --> 06:08.520
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

06:08.580 --> 06:10.450
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

06:10.360 --> 06:10.950
Xiahou Dan,

06:10.480 --> 06:12.950
♪ I never yielded ♪

06:11.720 --> 06:13.120
what on earth do you mean?

06:13.230 --> 06:14.730
♪ But why ♪

06:14.990 --> 06:19.480
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

06:15.190 --> 06:17.050
You drugged me without my consent

06:18.090 --> 06:19.910
and went to face Prince Duan alone.

06:19.910 --> 06:22.280
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

06:20.730 --> 06:22.560
You think you're very manly, huh?

06:22.330 --> 06:24.130
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

06:24.200 --> 06:26.510
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

06:26.600 --> 06:27.560
If you're so eager to play the hero,

06:26.870 --> 06:28.750
♪ The first time I met you ♪

06:28.950 --> 06:30.000
then go all the way.

06:29.100 --> 06:38.050
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

06:32.750 --> 06:34.810
Why do you have to make me come find Bai

06:35.000 --> 06:37.260
and be the commander of the Three Armies?

06:38.600 --> 06:39.560
Sometimes I really think

06:39.560 --> 06:41.690
you men are so strange and conflicted.

06:42.950 --> 06:44.880
You clearly don't want me to leave,

06:46.680 --> 06:47.870
yet you keep saying

06:48.750 --> 06:50.210
you're giving me a choice.

06:51.980 --> 06:53.110
♪ Blame me ♪

06:52.800 --> 06:54.560
It's really just that you don't want to
bear the consequences.

06:53.750 --> 06:57.250
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

06:56.750 --> 06:58.409
You want everything your way—

06:58.830 --> 06:59.560
you're sick,

06:58.870 --> 06:59.930
♪ Hide me ♪

07:00.610 --> 07:04.410
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

07:00.920 --> 07:02.250
and you need treatment.

07:05.740 --> 07:08.190
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

07:07.800 --> 07:08.600
You're right.

07:09.020 --> 07:11.630
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

07:12.580 --> 07:15.560
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

07:13.360 --> 07:14.040
I am sick,

07:15.580 --> 07:17.680
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

07:18.150 --> 07:20.570
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

07:18.190 --> 07:19.250
and it's terminal.

07:20.620 --> 07:22.380
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

07:22.410 --> 07:24.930
♪ I never yielded ♪

07:23.510 --> 07:25.040
I don't have much time left.

07:25.240 --> 07:26.760
♪ But why ♪

07:26.970 --> 07:31.460
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

07:29.780 --> 07:31.130
But I really,

07:31.870 --> 07:34.230
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

07:33.120 --> 07:33.920
really,

07:34.270 --> 07:36.120
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

07:36.170 --> 07:38.490
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

07:37.240 --> 07:38.720
really want you to love me.

07:38.960 --> 07:40.659
♪ The first time I met you ♪

07:41.250 --> 07:49.100
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

07:42.870 --> 07:44.400
But I also want you to leave,

07:47.800 --> 07:51.000
because I've only got
this little time left to be with you.

07:53.560 --> 07:54.900
But you're not dead yet,

07:55.190 --> 07:56.270
so shut up!

08:04.600 --> 08:05.480
Her Highness doesn't sound

08:05.480 --> 08:06.280
very pleased.

08:06.510 --> 08:08.170
Should we go in and soothe her?

08:09.120 --> 08:10.580
General, you may not know.

08:10.750 --> 08:11.930
This is not anger.

08:12.070 --> 08:13.320
If a woman's still willing to scold you,

08:13.320 --> 08:14.920
that means she's not given up on you.

08:14.920 --> 08:16.560
General, you may know
how to fight battles,

08:16.560 --> 08:18.560
but you don't know much about women.

08:21.680 --> 08:22.160
You all,

08:23.160 --> 08:24.090
keep watch here.

08:25.830 --> 08:26.310
You,

08:27.800 --> 08:29.600
go and notify everyone to gather

08:30.090 --> 08:32.419
at my Deputy General's tent
for a meeting.

08:33.390 --> 08:35.049
Tonight, before I go to sleep,

08:35.789 --> 08:36.919
no one is allowed to!

08:42.320 --> 08:43.250
He's flustered.

08:52.200 --> 08:52.910
Wanyin...

08:53.270 --> 08:54.130
Don't touch me.

08:57.480 --> 08:58.480
I know I was wrong.

09:02.630 --> 09:03.690
I won't do it again.

09:08.230 --> 09:08.770
I mean it.

09:15.480 --> 09:15.940
Wanyin.

09:17.750 --> 09:18.410
Yu.

09:25.510 --> 09:26.310
What's wrong?

09:27.200 --> 09:27.930
Are you hurt?

09:29.480 --> 09:29.870
No.

09:44.840 --> 09:46.770
Your head ailment flared up again?

09:49.000 --> 09:50.730
It flared up once along the way.

09:52.910 --> 09:54.040
That was why I missed

09:54.540 --> 09:56.800
the rendezvous with you guys in Peiyang.

09:59.750 --> 10:01.880
So what exactly happened on Mount Bei?

10:02.360 --> 10:03.960
Everyone said you were dead,

10:04.510 --> 10:06.110
but I just didn't believe it.

10:06.750 --> 10:08.680
After all, Mr. Bei was by your side.

10:10.270 --> 10:11.200
Where's Mr. Bei?

10:14.240 --> 10:16.600
The situation was critical at that moment.

10:16.600 --> 10:18.240
We were almost at a dead end.

10:19.000 --> 10:20.460
Rather than die together,

10:21.390 --> 10:23.450
I revealed my true identity to Mr. Bei

10:23.910 --> 10:25.240
and had him leave first.

10:30.030 --> 10:31.490
Mr. Bei treated us so well.

10:32.960 --> 10:34.480
If there's ever a chance,

10:36.650 --> 10:38.190
we must thank him in person.

10:45.920 --> 10:47.520
Once we reclaim the capital,

10:48.750 --> 10:50.150
I'll send Bai to find him.

10:52.290 --> 10:53.690
That's the best we can do.

10:57.510 --> 10:58.570
What are you doing?

10:59.270 --> 11:00.800
I haven't forgiven you yet.

11:05.440 --> 11:05.970
Yu.

11:07.580 --> 11:08.000
Yu.

11:08.790 --> 11:10.250
I really won't do it again.

11:10.630 --> 11:11.160
I swear it

11:12.000 --> 11:13.800
with the little life I have left.

11:14.030 --> 11:15.290
Who asked you to swear?

11:15.790 --> 11:16.450
Xiahou Dan,

11:16.500 --> 11:18.230
you want me to punch you or what?

11:22.910 --> 11:24.170
I won't swear anymore.

11:26.080 --> 11:26.680
I'm sorry.

11:28.670 --> 11:29.400
Don't be mad.

11:46.670 --> 11:47.080
You

11:47.960 --> 11:50.390
were all personally trained
by me, Lin Xuanying.

11:50.390 --> 11:52.190
I know you're loyal and devoted,

11:52.840 --> 11:55.040
and each of you can take on 10 opponents.

11:55.440 --> 11:57.500
But with these weapons in your hands,

11:57.750 --> 11:59.350
each of you could take on 100!

12:00.440 --> 12:01.440
During this time,

12:02.270 --> 12:03.400
we've been marching

12:04.240 --> 12:05.900
and training at the same time.

12:06.440 --> 12:07.510
By now, you all should fully understand

12:07.510 --> 12:09.440
the might of this sleeve crossbow.

12:10.000 --> 12:12.200
But now that we've reached the capital,

12:12.390 --> 12:15.250
you don't know exactly
who it's meant to be aimed at.

12:17.000 --> 12:18.930
You've probably already guessed—

12:19.440 --> 12:20.230
this weapon

12:20.690 --> 12:22.090
is meant for a rebellion!

12:22.550 --> 12:23.350
That's right.

12:24.510 --> 12:26.720
But it's a rebellion for the right cause,

12:26.720 --> 12:28.320
aimed against the traitors.

12:29.950 --> 12:31.720
I, Lin Xuanying,
Deputy General of the Right Army!

12:31.720 --> 12:33.200
I, Shen Xiao,
Commandant of the Right Army!

12:33.200 --> 12:34.840
I, Chi Yulin,
Colonel of the Right Army!

12:34.840 --> 12:37.000
I, Hulan Zhe'er, General of the Household
of the Right Army!

12:37.000 --> 12:38.200
Pay our respects to Your Majesty

12:38.200 --> 12:39.480
and Your Majesty the Empress!

12:39.480 --> 12:40.210
His Majesty?

12:41.320 --> 12:42.360
His Majesty is still alive?

12:42.360 --> 12:43.760
It's His Majesty indeed.

12:43.800 --> 12:45.910
When I returned to the capital
with General You to report our duties,

12:45.910 --> 12:47.440
I saw him in the palace hall.

12:47.550 --> 12:50.150
Then why did Prince Duan say
His Majesty had...

12:50.800 --> 12:52.460
Congratulations, everyone.

12:52.550 --> 12:54.200
You're about to earn the merit of
restoring the throne!

12:54.200 --> 12:57.750
Greetings, Your Majesty!
Greetings, Your Majesty the Empress!

12:57.750 --> 12:59.240
No need for formalities, gentlemen.

12:59.240 --> 13:02.170
-Thank you, Your Majesty!
-Thank you, Your Majesty!

13:09.870 --> 13:10.670
This weapon

13:11.930 --> 13:13.730
was made by an old friend of mine.

13:15.870 --> 13:16.600
Originally,

13:17.240 --> 13:18.440
he only hoped it could

13:19.120 --> 13:19.950
keep me safe.

13:22.720 --> 13:23.200
Today,

13:23.960 --> 13:25.360
I place this in your hands

13:25.750 --> 13:28.100
not in the hope of seizing power

13:28.510 --> 13:29.840
or reclaiming the throne,

13:29.840 --> 13:30.900
but in the hope that

13:32.110 --> 13:33.720
you can use it to safeguard our realm,

13:33.720 --> 13:34.780
protect our state,

13:35.240 --> 13:37.240
and ensure the safety of the people!

14:14.870 --> 14:16.390
This is the medicine prescribed by
Physician Xiao.

14:16.390 --> 14:17.320
How is Cen doing?

14:17.630 --> 14:18.160
Not well.

14:18.510 --> 14:20.240
He can't even get out of bed anymore.

14:20.240 --> 14:21.630
Don't let it show later.

14:22.080 --> 14:22.410
Okay.

14:22.480 --> 14:23.080
Come on in.

14:23.750 --> 14:24.600
Put on a smile.

14:38.910 --> 14:39.440
I'm back.

14:41.150 --> 14:42.480
I bought some live fish.

14:42.720 --> 14:43.920
I'll make you fish soup later

14:43.920 --> 14:45.780
to help you regain your strength.

14:47.160 --> 14:47.600
Cen.

14:48.030 --> 14:49.960
Was my divination accurate or not?

14:50.320 --> 14:52.760
I said it would snow today.

14:53.030 --> 14:53.510
And it's

14:53.870 --> 14:55.270
indeed snowing outside.

14:56.480 --> 14:56.810
Here.

14:58.030 --> 14:59.480
Then it was actually a pity

14:59.480 --> 15:01.280
that you were transferred out of

15:01.440 --> 15:03.300
the Imperial Observatory, Yang.

15:04.330 --> 15:05.630
You can even joke now.

15:06.320 --> 15:07.780
Are you almost recovered?

15:10.910 --> 15:12.170
Enough with the jokes.

15:14.030 --> 15:15.400
Yang meant well.

15:16.270 --> 15:17.600
I know

15:18.120 --> 15:19.080
my condition.

15:20.080 --> 15:21.810
No need to take it so seriously.

15:29.200 --> 15:30.260
Seriously though,

15:30.750 --> 15:32.480
what's the situation outside?

15:35.630 --> 15:36.200
Not good.

15:37.600 --> 15:39.510
We were right
not to return to our residences.

15:39.510 --> 15:41.700
The ministers who knelt outside
His Majesty's chambers

15:41.700 --> 15:44.360
have been trapped in their own residences
by the Imperial Guards

15:44.360 --> 15:45.960
and are not allowed to leave.

15:46.630 --> 15:48.340
His Majesty was prescient.

15:49.120 --> 15:49.850
This hideout

15:50.020 --> 15:51.550
he prepared for us back then

15:51.790 --> 15:52.320
has now

15:52.720 --> 15:53.780
become our refuge.

15:54.120 --> 15:57.080
What I'm worried about is that
given Prince Duan's methods,

15:57.080 --> 15:58.600
his men finding this place

15:58.720 --> 16:00.050
is only a matter of time.

16:01.270 --> 16:03.000
Since things have come to this,

16:03.710 --> 16:04.910
we should plan ahead.

16:15.150 --> 16:15.960
At this point,

16:16.360 --> 16:18.290
there are only two ways to survive:

16:19.710 --> 16:21.170
either resign from office

16:22.150 --> 16:22.840
or

16:23.480 --> 16:25.410
pledge allegiance to Prince Duan.

16:26.080 --> 16:27.410
But from the looks of it,

16:28.030 --> 16:29.560
you don't seem like the type

16:30.240 --> 16:32.300
to pledge allegiance to Prince Duan.

16:32.360 --> 16:32.960
Of course.

16:33.080 --> 16:34.240
I will never pledge allegiance.

16:34.240 --> 16:35.340
I'd rather spill my blood in the main hall

16:35.340 --> 16:36.600
and go down in history.

16:36.840 --> 16:37.320
True.

16:38.390 --> 16:39.720
I'm planning to resign.

16:41.030 --> 16:42.030
Now there's no one left in the court

16:42.030 --> 16:43.810
worth my loyalty.

16:44.440 --> 16:45.470
I might as well

16:46.240 --> 16:48.440
return home and take care of my parents.

16:51.240 --> 16:53.840
I'd actually like to
try pledging allegiance.

16:54.790 --> 16:55.320
Er Lan.

16:55.480 --> 16:57.050
Now is not the time for jokes.

16:57.050 --> 16:58.290
I'm not joking.

16:59.030 --> 17:00.290
With His Majesty dead,

17:00.790 --> 17:03.850
most royalists will choose to resign
to stay alive.

17:04.140 --> 17:06.240
There will be many vacancies in the court,

17:06.240 --> 17:08.160
and Prince Duan will need people
to work for him.

17:08.160 --> 17:09.290
So in the short term,

17:09.349 --> 17:11.680
he probably won't touch those who remain.

17:13.240 --> 17:14.900
Er, you're smarter than this.

17:15.349 --> 17:16.810
Even if he doesn't act now,

17:17.000 --> 17:19.160
how can we be sure Prince Duan
won't settle scores later?

17:19.160 --> 17:20.880
Let's take it one step at a time.

17:20.880 --> 17:22.200
When that time really comes,

17:22.200 --> 17:23.800
dying then won't be too late.

17:25.589 --> 17:28.040
Compared to dying in a show of loyalty,

17:29.640 --> 17:30.310
I think

17:30.640 --> 17:32.550
His Majesty would perhaps prefer to see

17:32.550 --> 17:34.120
us keeping the people safe

17:34.440 --> 17:36.350
and not letting them
suffer from the turmoil.

17:36.350 --> 17:38.210
Er, there's no need to insinuate.

17:39.200 --> 17:39.830
I am now

17:40.350 --> 17:42.830
no longer the hothead I was
when I first joined the court.

17:42.830 --> 17:45.560
Of course I understand
your good intentions, Er.

17:46.510 --> 17:47.310
It's just that

17:48.550 --> 17:49.610
at a time like this,

17:50.000 --> 17:51.960
pledging allegiance to
someone like Prince Duan

17:51.960 --> 17:53.490
and bowing my head to him...

17:54.510 --> 17:56.480
It would truly be a humiliation
beyond measure.

17:56.480 --> 17:58.310
As the saying goes,
when a mansion is about to collapse,

17:58.310 --> 18:00.770
the power of one person
is so insignificant.

18:00.920 --> 18:02.240
Life is short,

18:04.070 --> 18:06.270
and Er, you are in the prime of your life.

18:07.240 --> 18:09.170
Why not live for yourself for once?

18:20.790 --> 18:22.310
Cen, there's something you don't know.

18:22.310 --> 18:23.240
I'm staying

18:23.880 --> 18:25.540
not only for the greater good,

18:26.510 --> 18:28.310
but also for personal feelings.

18:37.000 --> 18:37.800
Wait a minute.

18:40.640 --> 18:42.440
Personal feelings?

18:48.400 --> 18:49.330
Which lady is it?

18:49.530 --> 18:50.720
Have we met her?

18:51.350 --> 18:52.310
It's his private matter.

18:52.310 --> 18:53.370
Why are you prying?

18:53.830 --> 18:55.230
But Er isn't an outsider.

18:55.750 --> 18:56.150
Right.

18:56.550 --> 18:58.400
Right, he... He isn't an outsider.

18:58.400 --> 18:59.000
Indeed, he isn't an outsider.

18:59.000 --> 18:59.790
Since he isn't an outsider,

18:59.790 --> 19:01.310
then let's not leave either.

19:01.310 --> 19:02.960
We can't let her be alone in the court,

19:02.960 --> 19:04.240
fighting a lone battle, right?

19:04.240 --> 19:05.400
Didn't you just say you'd rather

19:05.400 --> 19:07.830
spill your blood in the main hall
and go down in history?

19:07.830 --> 19:09.960
Why did you change your stance so fast?

19:10.870 --> 19:12.400
I never changed, okay? I...

19:12.590 --> 19:14.830
I do want to spill my blood
in the main hall.

19:14.830 --> 19:16.830
But since I want to spill my blood there,

19:16.830 --> 19:18.440
I have to get to the main hall first,
right?

19:18.440 --> 19:19.750
I can't spill my blood at...

19:19.750 --> 19:20.480
At the entrance, right?

19:20.480 --> 19:21.640
You... Wait a second.

19:21.640 --> 19:22.920
W-What about me?

19:23.070 --> 19:24.940
How dare you, Yang Duojie?

19:25.160 --> 19:26.360
A-At a time like this,

19:26.400 --> 19:27.730
everyone is sad.

19:29.310 --> 19:31.440
What about me? Don't say another word.

19:34.920 --> 19:36.780
I originally wanted this fish...

20:01.550 --> 20:04.350
Actually, it would be safer for you
to stay in Peiyang to hold the fort.

20:04.350 --> 20:06.200
After the turmoil in the city
settles down...

20:06.200 --> 20:07.350
Don't even think about it.

20:07.350 --> 20:09.680
I won't let you have your way
a second time.

20:11.880 --> 20:12.680
Don't you want

20:12.830 --> 20:14.030
to travel the world anymore?

20:14.030 --> 20:14.720
I do.

20:15.960 --> 20:17.350
The world is right there.

20:17.350 --> 20:19.350
It doesn't matter if I go a bit later.

20:22.480 --> 20:23.540
Come to think of it,

20:24.440 --> 20:27.400
we've only known each other
for a little over half a year,

20:27.400 --> 20:29.000
yet so much has happened.

20:31.920 --> 20:32.980
We've practically

20:33.030 --> 20:35.160
gone through life and death together.

20:35.240 --> 20:35.860
However,

20:36.750 --> 20:38.070
in a sense,

20:39.000 --> 20:40.860
it seems like we've only just met?

20:41.590 --> 20:42.030
Yeah.

20:43.550 --> 20:45.880
After all, you don't even know
my name yet.

20:47.640 --> 20:49.300
I had my own worries back then,

20:49.400 --> 20:52.530
so I didn't dare to discuss this topic
with you in detail.

20:52.790 --> 20:54.190
So what is your real name?

20:54.920 --> 20:55.650
My name is...

21:03.210 --> 21:05.550
Don't you think the name Yu Wanyin
sounds really nice?

21:05.550 --> 21:07.110
I do think Yu Wanyin sounds very nice.

21:07.110 --> 21:08.510
So what is your real name?

21:09.110 --> 21:09.370
I...

21:09.620 --> 21:10.860
I can tell you,

21:11.350 --> 21:13.350
but you have to promise me one thing.

21:13.350 --> 21:13.950
What is it?

21:15.130 --> 21:16.930
You can't laugh after I tell you.

21:20.030 --> 21:21.030
Why would I laugh?

21:21.720 --> 21:23.650
Could it be funnier than Zhang San?

21:25.440 --> 21:26.170
Wang Cuihua.

21:36.110 --> 21:36.680
For real?

21:40.900 --> 21:42.560
Your real name is Wang Cuihua?

21:45.280 --> 21:46.620
Wang Cuihua...

21:49.680 --> 21:50.210
"Cuihua,

21:50.790 --> 21:52.390
serve the pickled cabbage!"

21:54.440 --> 21:55.750
My third great-uncle gave me that name.

21:55.750 --> 21:57.350
So now you know why I hate him.

21:58.150 --> 22:00.950
Your third great-uncle
sure had a knack for names.

22:03.790 --> 22:04.680
Wang Cuihua...

22:05.920 --> 22:07.920
No wonder you put off mentioning it.

22:08.720 --> 22:10.640
I'll get angry if you keep laughing.

22:10.640 --> 22:11.680
Alright, alright.

22:11.680 --> 22:12.810
I'll stop laughing.

22:16.790 --> 22:17.830
It seems the two of us

22:17.830 --> 22:19.530
are pretty evenly matched—

22:19.880 --> 22:21.080
hard to tell who wins.

22:22.240 --> 22:24.640
I don't even mind
you're a middle schooler.

22:24.750 --> 22:27.150
I'm technically robbing the cradle, okay?

22:27.690 --> 22:29.690
What do you mean robbing the cradle?

22:30.160 --> 22:32.310
Yes, I was a middle schooler
when I transmigrated here,

22:32.310 --> 22:34.110
but I've spent over 10 years in this book.

22:34.110 --> 22:36.070
We didn't transmigrate at the same time
after all.

22:36.070 --> 22:37.440
Which year did you come from?

22:37.440 --> 22:38.000
2016.

22:38.720 --> 22:39.720
I'm from the year 2025.

22:39.720 --> 22:40.000
See?

22:43.110 --> 22:44.400
No wonder.

22:45.590 --> 22:47.130
When we chatted before,

22:47.270 --> 22:49.000
all your jokes were so old-fashioned,

22:49.000 --> 22:49.480
like

22:50.240 --> 22:51.640
"blue skinny mushroom,"

22:51.720 --> 22:53.550
and "Yuanfang, what do you think?"

22:53.550 --> 22:55.480
I felt something was off back then.

22:57.400 --> 22:58.930
Since we're on the subject,

23:00.350 --> 23:01.880
I want to ask you something.

23:03.310 --> 23:05.510
What is the "smell of work"?

23:06.880 --> 23:07.760
And that saying

23:07.830 --> 23:09.350
"city or not"—

23:09.830 --> 23:10.830
what does it mean?

23:12.350 --> 23:14.000
And that thing you always say—

23:14.000 --> 23:15.460
"Zize"—what does it mean?

23:17.440 --> 23:18.170
Want to know?

23:19.200 --> 23:20.400
Then repeat after me.

23:21.070 --> 23:22.440
Tell me wh-what it means first.

23:22.440 --> 23:24.110
J-Just repeat after me first.

23:25.160 --> 23:26.020
Fine. Teach me.

23:28.310 --> 23:28.790
Zize.

23:30.550 --> 23:31.030
Zize.

23:32.750 --> 23:33.640
Zize.

23:35.240 --> 23:36.050
Zize.

23:37.590 --> 23:38.590
What does it mean?

23:39.030 --> 23:42.290
It just sounds similar to "jiejie,"
meaning older sister.

23:43.280 --> 23:43.910
Got it?

23:44.640 --> 23:45.680
Then what about those other things,

23:45.680 --> 23:47.070
like "laying low"
and "winner winner, chicken dinner"?

23:47.070 --> 23:48.590
You don't know those either?

23:48.590 --> 23:49.060
I don't.

23:49.350 --> 23:51.610
Then why did you lay low with me
last time?

23:51.880 --> 23:53.720
I saw you were so fired up,

23:53.790 --> 23:56.190
so I didn't have the heart
to interrupt you.

23:56.590 --> 23:57.480
Little brat.

23:58.240 --> 24:00.370
And that... What's it called again...

24:00.590 --> 24:01.810
OOC?

24:01.880 --> 24:02.630
And that

24:03.750 --> 24:05.530
"attention seeker"—

24:06.000 --> 24:06.680
what does it mean?

24:06.680 --> 24:08.540
I'll tell you what that one means.

24:08.950 --> 24:11.480
You're the definition of
an attention seeker.

24:11.480 --> 24:12.880
I'm the definition of an attention seeker?

24:12.880 --> 24:14.000
You're an attention seeker.

24:14.000 --> 24:14.550
Remember?

24:14.550 --> 24:15.400
I'm an attention seeker.

24:15.400 --> 24:16.660
T-Then what about you?

24:38.510 --> 24:38.960
Cen.

24:39.110 --> 24:39.810
Sorry.

24:39.920 --> 24:40.920
Why are you awake?

24:41.270 --> 24:42.330
Sorry I woke you up.

24:49.720 --> 24:51.720
Physician Xiao's medicine worked.

24:52.270 --> 24:53.720
You look much better.

24:56.110 --> 24:56.750
I want to,

24:57.480 --> 24:58.480
while I still can,

24:59.070 --> 25:00.550
make a trip back to my courtyard

25:00.550 --> 25:02.010
and check on my Yan millet.

25:04.160 --> 25:05.240
But right now,

25:05.480 --> 25:06.790
it's snowing heavily outside.

25:06.790 --> 25:08.120
With your condition...

25:09.350 --> 25:10.350
If I don't go now,

25:14.440 --> 25:16.640
I'm afraid I won't have another chance.

25:40.730 --> 25:41.160
I...

25:42.310 --> 25:42.590
I...

25:44.510 --> 25:45.440
I'll go with you.

25:47.000 --> 25:47.400
Okay.

26:03.480 --> 26:04.720
If everything goes well,

26:04.720 --> 26:05.980
by this time tomorrow,

26:06.350 --> 26:07.880
we'll have a bed to sleep in.

26:08.440 --> 26:11.040
We'll send someone
to bring Mr. Bei back later.

26:11.680 --> 26:13.010
Now that Bai is here too,

26:13.240 --> 26:15.400
our hotpot for four can reopen.

26:23.270 --> 26:23.870
By the way.

26:24.510 --> 26:26.480
that Xiao Tiancai is still in the palace.

26:26.480 --> 26:27.400
Before I left,

26:28.110 --> 26:30.400
I suggested the idea of
fighting poison with poison to him,

26:30.400 --> 26:31.930
and he said it was feasible.

26:32.110 --> 26:33.340
Maybe by now,

26:33.440 --> 26:35.980
he's already made a breakthrough
in his research.

26:35.980 --> 26:38.190
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

26:38.480 --> 26:39.730
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

26:40.060 --> 26:42.200
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

26:40.880 --> 26:42.580
I almost forgot about those scholars.

26:42.580 --> 26:43.900
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

26:43.480 --> 26:44.750
Prince Duan won't give them a hard time,
will he?

26:43.990 --> 26:46.350
♪ Words unspoken ♪

26:45.590 --> 26:47.320
Er Lan and Yang Duojie are fine,

26:47.440 --> 26:49.080
but I'm really worried about Li Yunxi.

26:47.920 --> 26:50.400
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

26:49.510 --> 26:51.480
He risks his life to remonstrate
at every turn.

26:51.480 --> 26:52.390
If that happens,

26:52.050 --> 26:54.230
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

26:52.510 --> 26:53.590
and he risks his life
to remonstrate again,

26:53.590 --> 26:54.410
Prince Duan will...

26:54.410 --> 26:55.550
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

26:55.910 --> 26:57.960
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

26:57.550 --> 26:58.410
Don't worry, Wanyin.

26:58.410 --> 26:59.790
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

26:59.550 --> 27:00.200
Everything will go well.

27:00.000 --> 27:02.380
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

27:01.920 --> 27:02.500
I'm here.

27:03.990 --> 27:07.290
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

27:07.890 --> 27:11.270
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

27:11.970 --> 27:14.980
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

27:15.470 --> 27:17.300
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

27:15.920 --> 27:16.850
I believe in you.

27:17.520 --> 27:19.230
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

27:19.460 --> 27:21.200
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

27:21.410 --> 27:23.520
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

27:24.010 --> 27:27.080
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

27:28.000 --> 27:30.340
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

27:30.460 --> 27:31.550
♪ Still unchanged ♪

27:32.000 --> 27:34.900
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

27:35.490 --> 27:36.950
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

27:37.070 --> 27:44.320
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

27:55.900 --> 27:59.460
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

28:08.550 --> 28:10.210
What have the plants ever done

28:13.590 --> 28:15.050
to deserve such disaster?

28:16.270 --> 28:19.310
Fortunately, the spring breeze
will bring them back to life.

28:19.310 --> 28:21.110
Cen, you needn't lament so much.

28:22.070 --> 28:22.880
Yeah.

28:24.310 --> 28:25.640
When I was born,

28:26.350 --> 28:29.010
I was already afflicted with
a serious illness.

28:29.880 --> 28:32.110
I knew I wouldn't live long.

28:40.830 --> 28:42.200
Yet, I've always admired how plants,

28:42.200 --> 28:43.730
though seemingly fragile,

28:44.920 --> 28:46.780
are actually full of resilience.

28:47.160 --> 28:50.110
Compared to humans' mere few decades
of lifespan,

28:50.720 --> 28:53.320
plants can return to life
season after season.

28:54.160 --> 28:55.490
As long as there's wind,

28:55.680 --> 28:56.350
rain,

28:57.110 --> 28:57.920
and soil,

28:58.720 --> 29:00.160
they can grow freely

29:01.200 --> 29:02.110
and joyfully.

29:03.480 --> 29:04.940
But humans are not plants—

29:05.030 --> 29:06.690
how could we live in solitude?

29:07.070 --> 29:08.000
Cen,

29:08.480 --> 29:10.410
you've grown close to us after all.

29:13.440 --> 29:15.900
If it weren't for you guys
dragging me along,

29:15.920 --> 29:18.270
not minding my coldness and frailty,

29:18.960 --> 29:21.690
not looking down on
my dullness and awkwardness,

29:22.350 --> 29:23.750
I truly wouldn't know

29:24.920 --> 29:27.000
what I've missed all these years.

29:34.920 --> 29:35.640
Er Lan,

29:36.790 --> 29:37.830
did you know

29:38.400 --> 29:39.240
that Li

29:39.830 --> 29:41.440
used to look down on you?

29:41.920 --> 29:42.550
But now,

29:43.790 --> 29:45.250
he's sincerely convinced

29:45.750 --> 29:47.750
and holds you in the highest regard.

29:48.110 --> 29:50.490
And for a long time,
Yang had quite a few complaints

29:50.490 --> 29:53.050
about the fortune-teller position
at the Imperial Astronomer,

29:53.050 --> 29:54.640
and he often came to me to vent.

29:54.640 --> 29:55.070
Also,

29:55.590 --> 29:57.310
before Wang Zhao went on his mission,

29:57.310 --> 29:58.710
he asked me to take care of

29:58.790 --> 30:00.880
a lady selling tofu in the East Alley.

30:02.550 --> 30:03.510
That's a secret

30:05.590 --> 30:07.990
he'll never have the chance
to say out loud.

30:15.440 --> 30:16.570
Since it's a secret,

30:18.310 --> 30:19.480
why are you

30:20.050 --> 30:21.450
telling me about it, Cen?

30:24.590 --> 30:25.960
I'll be counting on you,

30:30.350 --> 30:33.210
Er Lan, to take care of these old friends
from now on.

30:45.440 --> 30:46.000
Okay.

30:50.070 --> 30:51.200
You have my promise.

30:52.400 --> 30:53.240
Then, Cen,

30:55.920 --> 30:57.750
would you like to hear my secret?

30:59.750 --> 31:01.640
For a secret to be a secret,

31:03.790 --> 31:06.190
it's best if the other person
doesn't know.

31:15.480 --> 31:16.940
If humans were like plants

31:19.000 --> 31:20.200
and had an afterlife,

31:23.440 --> 31:24.570
would you then, Cen?

31:30.510 --> 31:31.770
If there is a next life,

31:33.920 --> 31:35.720
I'd definitely play the zither,

31:36.240 --> 31:37.030
brew wine,

31:40.030 --> 31:41.690
and listen attentively to it.

32:42.690 --> 32:45.650
[Luo]

32:51.490 --> 32:53.270
[You]

32:57.830 --> 33:00.820
[Hai]

33:07.230 --> 33:11.350
[You]

33:14.380 --> 33:16.070
[Luo]

33:16.160 --> 33:17.480
[Hai]

33:24.270 --> 33:25.900
[Capital of Xia]

33:35.270 --> 33:36.000
General Luo,

33:36.310 --> 33:37.400
Deputy General Lin,

33:37.400 --> 33:38.480
Deputy General Zhou.

33:38.480 --> 33:39.960
Long time no see.

33:40.790 --> 33:41.400
Lord Jia.

33:42.240 --> 33:44.370
We've been waiting here for half a day.

33:44.530 --> 33:46.640
Why haven't the soldiers been allowed
into the city yet?

33:46.640 --> 33:47.100
Indeed.

33:47.790 --> 33:50.510
We came at urgent summons,
traveling day and night.

33:50.510 --> 33:52.170
But judging by the situation,

33:52.200 --> 33:53.730
it seems no one's in a hurry.

33:54.030 --> 33:55.510
You jest, Generals.

33:55.750 --> 33:58.510
His Highness indeed
has important matters to discuss,

33:58.510 --> 34:00.660
so he sent us here to receive you.

34:01.160 --> 34:01.960
That's right.

34:02.070 --> 34:02.720
Generals,

34:03.270 --> 34:06.230
please follow me
and enter the city alone first.

34:06.480 --> 34:07.520
Just us?

34:07.880 --> 34:09.000
What about the main troops?

34:09.000 --> 34:09.659
Never mind.

34:10.960 --> 34:12.800
Since this is His Highness's order,

34:12.800 --> 34:14.300
we shall obey.

34:15.230 --> 34:16.630
Li Zhong! You stay.

34:17.000 --> 34:17.760
-Yang Yi!
-Yes!

34:17.760 --> 34:19.000
Take a squad and come with me.

34:19.000 --> 34:20.130
The rest, stand by!

34:28.760 --> 34:29.909
Please, generals,

34:30.030 --> 34:31.489
kindly remove your swords

34:31.630 --> 34:32.840
before entering the city.

34:32.840 --> 34:33.770
What do you mean?

34:34.320 --> 34:35.290
We led the armies

34:35.440 --> 34:37.060
all the way here to help.

34:37.480 --> 34:39.670
Is this the courtesy
His Highness Prince Duan shows us?

34:39.670 --> 34:41.400
Generals, please don't
take this the wrong way.

34:41.400 --> 34:42.280
It's just that

34:42.550 --> 34:44.110
the situation inside the city

34:44.110 --> 34:45.370
is delicate right now,

34:45.710 --> 34:47.510
with spies from all sides mingling.

34:47.510 --> 34:48.710
Removing your swords

34:49.440 --> 34:51.230
is merely a formality.

34:51.280 --> 34:52.230
Yes, indeed.

34:52.760 --> 34:55.730
His Highness has prepared
a grand feast in the city,

34:56.000 --> 34:58.620
waiting to welcome you generals

34:58.800 --> 35:00.400
and reward the Three Armies.

35:02.400 --> 35:03.450
You lot

35:03.800 --> 35:05.070
are so twisted

35:05.480 --> 35:06.480
and troublesome.

35:08.860 --> 35:10.260
I have nothing to hide.

35:10.550 --> 35:11.810
If you want the swords,

35:12.030 --> 35:12.800
take them.

35:38.760 --> 35:39.490
You stay here

35:39.640 --> 35:41.570
and keep an eye on the Three Armies.

35:45.510 --> 35:48.360
Didn't Prince Duan himself
summon the Three Armies?

35:48.360 --> 35:50.820
Why won't he let the soldiers
enter the city?

35:56.280 --> 35:57.150
He is

35:57.510 --> 35:58.840
extremely suspicious.

35:59.440 --> 36:00.300
Could it be that

36:02.280 --> 36:04.940
there's some rift
between him and the soldiers?

36:04.960 --> 36:06.760
But what kind of rift could it be?

36:18.660 --> 36:23.900
[Memorial Tablet of Emperor Xiaohewen
of Great Xia]

36:26.920 --> 36:27.780
Your Highness.

36:29.160 --> 36:30.150
This man

36:32.550 --> 36:34.680
was sent by the Central Army back then,

36:35.710 --> 36:36.550
right?

36:37.230 --> 36:38.030
That's right,

36:38.440 --> 36:39.300
Your Highness.

36:39.960 --> 36:40.780
They also said

36:41.400 --> 36:42.930
General Luo's trusted aide

36:43.230 --> 36:44.960
interrogated him personally.

36:46.190 --> 36:48.590
They sent me an imposter.

36:52.090 --> 36:53.440
How amusing.

36:54.550 --> 36:55.680
This man's disguise

36:56.150 --> 36:57.630
was flawless.

36:59.110 --> 37:00.490
Perhaps General Luo,

37:00.630 --> 37:01.680
like us,

37:01.840 --> 37:03.510
was kept completely in the dark?

37:03.510 --> 37:04.520
The Three Armies

37:05.190 --> 37:07.000
have always been
under Your Highness's command.

37:07.000 --> 37:07.280
And

37:07.510 --> 37:08.360
General Luo

37:09.030 --> 37:11.240
has technically been through
life and death with you.

37:11.240 --> 37:12.710
He shouldn't have acted like that, right?

37:12.710 --> 37:15.240
If there were so many "shoulds"
in this world,

37:18.190 --> 37:20.470
Xiahou Dan should've long been dead!

37:20.920 --> 37:22.050
Yes, Your Highness.

37:34.320 --> 37:35.780
What do the craftsmen say?

37:38.070 --> 37:39.330
Can they replicate it?

37:39.920 --> 37:40.800
This object

37:41.030 --> 37:43.230
is designed with exquisite ingenuity.

37:43.510 --> 37:45.970
If we want to produce it
in large quantities,

37:46.030 --> 37:47.560
it'll still take some time.

37:58.760 --> 37:59.620
Your Highness,

37:59.800 --> 38:01.200
please be extra careful.

38:01.230 --> 38:02.920
This object is very dangerous.

38:02.920 --> 38:04.230
Don't let it hurt you.

38:05.580 --> 38:07.270
There's only one bullet left.

38:09.840 --> 38:10.570
Minister Wu.

38:11.510 --> 38:11.900
Yes.

38:12.670 --> 38:13.710
Take a guess—

38:15.110 --> 38:17.110
whose body will it pierce?

38:18.030 --> 38:19.030
Your Highness...

38:32.510 --> 38:33.370
Take them away.

38:36.550 --> 38:37.480
What's going on?

38:41.030 --> 38:43.480
The Imperial Guards are searching
the Three Armies one by one.

38:43.480 --> 38:45.830
I saw that they've selected some people

38:45.880 --> 38:47.670
from both the Left and Central Armies.
They seem to be

38:47.670 --> 38:51.130
-searching for suspicious individuals.
-Take this one away.

38:52.000 --> 38:52.840
You've got sharp eyes.

38:52.840 --> 38:53.590
Hurry up and check

38:53.590 --> 38:55.440
what criteria they are using
to select people.

38:55.440 --> 38:55.970
This one.

38:56.030 --> 38:56.830
Take him away.

38:57.280 --> 38:58.790
They seem to be picking out

38:59.840 --> 39:01.900
-the short and the weak.
-Move along.

39:03.920 --> 39:04.650
Turn around.

39:05.630 --> 39:07.000
Short points to you...

39:07.280 --> 39:08.080
Take him away.

39:08.400 --> 39:09.840
And weak points to me.

39:11.260 --> 39:12.060
Take him away.

39:15.670 --> 39:16.480
So Xiahou Bo...

39:16.480 --> 39:17.070
Take this one away too.

39:17.070 --> 39:19.070
Still hasn't given up on finding us.

39:21.230 --> 39:22.880
Luckily, our elite soldiers with guns

39:22.880 --> 39:24.440
-are all tall and strong.
-Take him away.

39:24.440 --> 39:27.700
They shouldn't fall within
the range of their inspection.

39:28.110 --> 39:29.110
Is there anything on our carriage

39:29.110 --> 39:30.570
that could cause trouble?

39:31.200 --> 39:33.400
All the weapons have been distributed.

39:33.550 --> 39:34.110
Take him away.

39:34.110 --> 39:35.000
There's some spare gunpowder

39:35.000 --> 39:36.660
hidden underneath the grain.

39:36.840 --> 39:38.710
But if they conduct a deliberate search,

39:38.710 --> 39:40.280
there's still a risk of it
being discovered.

39:40.280 --> 39:40.940
This is bad.

39:42.880 --> 39:44.680
There's squad heading this way.

39:44.920 --> 39:47.920
-They might want to search our carriage.
-Move along.

39:49.150 --> 39:49.880
Turn around.

39:53.320 --> 39:54.280
We can't wait for Bai anymore.

39:54.280 --> 39:55.000
Let's make our move.

39:55.000 --> 39:55.460
Hold on.

39:56.880 --> 39:57.440
I have an idea.
